assified into the\nNegative and Very Negative classes. As a use-case, we try to explore the\nflaming phenomena in the news media domain and therefore we focused on news\nitems posted by three popular news media on Facebook (BBCNews, CNN and FoxNews)\nto train and test the model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Sep 2019 13:19:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-17"}
